Standard Bank Unit Agrees $60 Million Loan for Gold Fields Ghana Operation

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-06-27T13:12:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-27/standard-bank-unit-agrees-60-million-loan-for-gold-fields-ghana-operation.html
Standard Bank Group Ltd.’s Ghanaian
unit said it signed a $60 million loan agreement with  Gold
Fields Ltd. (GFI) ’s operation in the West African country.  The three-year revolving loan will be used by Gold Fields
Ghana Ltd. to replace its fleet at its Tarkwa and Abosso mines,
Johannesburg-based Standard Bank said in an e-mailed statement
today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
